amp;_pre&gt;div]:bg-bg-000/50 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-0.5 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-border-400 [&amp;_.ignore-pre-bg&gt;div]:bg-transparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Right — Docker on your local Windows machine shuts down when you close it or sleep. For 24/7 you need a cloud server. Cheapest options:</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Free tier (good for testing):</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Railway.app</strong> — free tier, deploy from GitHub, easiest setup</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Render.com</strong> — free tier with auto-sleep (wakes on message, slight delay)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Oracle Cloud</strong> — always-free VM (best free option for 24/7)</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Cheap paid ($4-6/month):</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Hetzner</strong> — €3.79/month, best value</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>DigitalOcean</strong> — $4/month droplet</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>AWS Lightsail</strong> — $3.50/month</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Want me to set up deployment for one of these? Railway is the fastest — just push to GitHub and it runs. Or if you want a proper always-on VM, I can write the setup script for Hetzner/DigitalOcean.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
