-0.5 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-border-400 [&amp;_.ignore-pre-bg&gt;div]:bg-transparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="grid grid-rows-[auto_auto] min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 min-w-0"><div class="min-w-0 pl-2 py-1.5"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><button class="group/status flex items-center gap-2 py-1 text-sm transition-colors cursor-pointer text-left text-text-500 hover:text-text-300 flex-1 min-w-0" aria-expanded="false"><div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 min-w-0" style="opacity: 1;"><span class="truncate text-sm font-base">Searched the web</span><span class="inline-flex transition-transform duration-200 shrink-0 -rotate-90"><div style="width: 12px; height: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M14.128 7.165a.502.502 0 0 1 .744.67l-4.5 5-.078.07a.5.5 0 0 1-.666-.07l-4.5-5-.06-.082a.501.501 0 0 1 .729-.656l.075.068L10 11.752z"></path></svg></div></span></div></button></div><span class="sr-only" role="status" aria-live="polite">Searched the web</span><div class="grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-out" style="grid-template-rows: 0fr;"><div class="overflow-hidden min-w-0"></div></div></div></div><div class="row-start-2 col-start-1 relative grid isolate min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 relative z-[2] min-w-0"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Here's the honest breakdown:</p>
<div class="overflow-x-auto w-full px-2 mb-6"><table class="min-w-full border-collapse text-sm leading-[1.7] whitespace-normal"><thead class="text-left"><tr><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Platform</th><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Free Tier</th><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Credit Card</th><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">24/7?</th><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Good for Zarik?</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><strong>Render</strong></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Free web services, sleeps after 15min idle</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">No card needed</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">No — wakes on request (~1min delay)</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Telegram bot will miss messages while sleeping</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><strong>Railway</strong></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">$5 one-time credit, 30 days</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">No card needed</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Only until credits run out</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Bot dies after ~1 week</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><strong>Fly.io</strong></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">No free tier anymore</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Card required</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">—</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">—</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><strong>Oracle Cloud</strong></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Always-free VM, 24GB RAM</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Card required (won't charge)</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Yes, true 24/7</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Best option</td></tr></tbody></table></div>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">The problem is Zarik is a <strong>Telegram bot</strong> — it needs to be always polling for messages. Render's free web services sleep after 15 minutes of inactivity, which means your bot goes offline and misses messages. Railway's free plan provides $5 in the first month and then $1 of credit per month — when credits run out, services pause. <span class="inline-flex" data-state="closed"><a href="https://encore.dev/articles/render-vs-railway" target="_blank" class="group/tag relative h-[18px] rounded-full inline-flex items-center overflow-hidden -translate-y-px cursor-pointer"><span class="relative transition-colors h-full max-w-[180px] overflow-hidden px-1.5 inline-flex items-center font-small rounded-full border-0.5 border-border-300 bg-bg-200 group-hover/tag:bg-accent-900 group-hover/tag:border-accent-100/60"><span class="text-nowrap text-text-300 break-all truncate font-normal group-hover/tag:text-text-200">Encore</span></span><span class="transition-all opacity-[0%] h-[17px] absolute right-[0.5px] inline rounded-r-full flex items-center px-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-900/0 via-accent-900/100 via-30% to-accent-900/100 group-hover/tag:opacity-[100%]"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="transition-all group-hover/tag:ease-out duration-[500ms] ease-in text-accent-100 group-hover/tag:scale-[100%] scale-[80%] group-hover/tag:opacity-[100%] opacity-[0%] -mr-[2px]"><path d="M200,64V168a8,8,0,0,1-16,0V83.31L69.66,197.66a8,8,0,0,1-11.32-11.32L172.69,72H88a8,8,0,0,1,0-16H192A8,8,0,0,1,200,64Z"></path></svg></span></a></span><span class="inline-flex w-1"></span><span class="inline-flex" data-state="closed"><a href="https://render.com/articles/platforms-with-a-real-free-tier-for-developers-in-2026" target="_blank" class="group/tag relative h-[18px] rounded-full inline-flex items-center overflow-hidden -translate-y-px cursor-pointer"><span class="relative transition-colors h-full max-w-[180px] overflow-hidden px-1.5 inline-flex items-center font-small rounded-full border-0.5 border-border-300 bg-bg-200 group-hover/tag:bg-accent-900 group-hover/tag:border-accent-100/60"><span class="text-nowrap text-text-300 break-all truncate font-normal group-hover/tag:text-text-200">Render</span></span><span class="transition-all opacity-[0%] h-[17px] absolute right-[0.5px] inline rounded-r-full flex items-center px-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-900/0 via-accent-900/100 via-30% to-accent-900/100 group-hover/tag:opacity-[100%]"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="transition-all group-hover/tag:ease-out duration-[500ms] ease-in text-accent-100 group-hover/tag:scale-[100%] scale-[80%] group-hover/tag:opacity-[100%] opacity-[0%] -mr-[2px]"><path d="M200,64V168a8,8,0,0,1-16,0V83.31L69.66,197.66a8,8,0,0,1-11.32-11.32L172.69,72H88a8,8,0,0,1,0-16H192A8,8,0,0,1,200,64Z"></path></svg></span></a></span></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>My honest recommendation:</strong> For a Telegram bot that needs to be always-on, none of the no-card free tiers work reliably. Your two real options are:</p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Keep running Docker on your PC</strong> with <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">--restart=always</code> and Windows set to never sleep — free, works now</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Oracle Cloud free tier</strong> — needs a card for verification but genuinely never charges. It's the only real free 24/7 option</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">If you want to test on Render/Railway first just to demo it, Railway is the easiest — sign up with GitHub, connect your repo, add env vars, and it runs. But know it'll stop after the credits expire.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
