"token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">\</span><span>Users</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">\</span><span>adars</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">\</span><span>OneDrive</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">\</span><span>Desktop</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">\</span><span>Zarik-travel_agent
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(112, 184, 255);">git</span><span> init
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(112, 184, 255);">git</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(112, 184, 255);">add</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(251, 173, 96);">.</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(112, 184, 255);">git</span><span> commit -m </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(155, 233, 99);">"zarik v1"</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(112, 184, 255);">git</span><span> branch -M main
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(112, 184, 255);">git</span><span> remote </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(112, 184, 255);">add</span><span> origin https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/zarik.git
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(112, 184, 255);">git</span><span> push -u origin main</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Step 2 — Deploy on Railway</strong></p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Go to <a class="underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current" href="https://railway.app/">railway.app</a> → sign up with GitHub (no card needed for trial)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click <strong>New Project</strong> → <strong>Deploy from GitHub Repo</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Select your <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">zarik</code> repo</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Railway auto-detects Python — it'll start building</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Step 3 — Add Environment Variables</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">In your Railway project dashboard → click your service → <strong>Variables</strong> tab → add these one by one:</p>
