leading-[1.7]">Drop it in your project root, replacing any existing README. Then for the GitHub <strong>About</strong> section (the description that shows under your repo name), go to your repo → click the gear icon next to "About" and paste:</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Description:</strong></p>
<blockquote class="ml-2 border-l-4 border-border-300/10 pl-4 text-text-300">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">AI-powered Telegram bot for travel agencies — generates personalized itineraries through natural conversation, manages leads in Excel, and remembers returning users. Built with LangGraph, Groq, FastAPI.</p>
</blockquote>
