span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> 🌍 Zarik Wiki</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span>Welcome to the Zarik documentation — an AI-powered travel itinerary assistant built for travel agencies.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span class="token token bold content" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">[</span><span class="token token bold content" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">Try the bot →</span><span class="token token bold content" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">](</span><span class="token token bold content" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">https://t.me/zzzarik_bot</span><span class="token token bold content" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">)</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
