</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">[</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data content" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">How It Works</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">](</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">How-It-Works</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">)</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Architecture, agent flow, and conversation lifecycle </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">[</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data content" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">Configuration</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">](</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">Configuration</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">)</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Environment variables, model selection, and tuning </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">[</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data content" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">Lead Management</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">](</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">Lead-Management</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">)</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Excel structure, status tracking, and API endpoints </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">[</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data content" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">Memory System</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">](</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">Memory-System</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">)</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Per-user memory, personalization, and data format </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">[</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data content" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">Deployment</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">](</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">Deployment</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">)</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Docker, Railway, and Oracle Cloud setup </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">[</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data content" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">Troubleshooting</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">](</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">Troubleshooting</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">)</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows table-data"> Common errors and fixes </span><span class="token token table table-data-rows" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">|</span><span class="token token table table-data-rows">
</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> What is Zarik?</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span>Zarik is a Telegram bot that acts as a travel agency's first point of contact. When a user messages the bot, it:
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">1.</span><span> </span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Greets</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span> them — recognizes returning users from memory
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">2.</span><span> </span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Collects preferences</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span> — destination, dates, budget, group size, interests through natural conversation
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">3.</span><span> </span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Generates an itinerary</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span> — detailed day-by-day plan with costs, food recommendations, and tips
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">4.</span><span> </span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Captures the lead</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span> — auto-saves everything to a formatted Excel sheet
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">5.</span><span> </span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Handles modifications</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span> — "add more street food", "make it cheaper", "swap day 3 and 4"
</span></span><span>
</span><span>All powered by a LangGraph stateful agent running Llama 3.3 70B via Groq.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> Tech Stack at a Glance</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">-</span><span> </span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Agent:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span> LangGraph + LangChain
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">-</span><span> </span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">LLM:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span> Groq API (Llama 3.3 70B Versatile)
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">-</span><span> </span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Backend:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span> FastAPI
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">-</span><span> </span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Client:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span> Telegram (python-telegram-bot)
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">-</span><span> </span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Leads:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span> Excel via openpyxl
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">-</span><span> </span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Memory:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span> Per-user JSON files</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
