span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> Getting Started</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> Prerequisites</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">-</span><span> Python 3.11+
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">-</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">[</span><span class="token token content" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">Groq API key</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">](</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">https://console.groq.com/keys</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">)</span><span> (free)
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">-</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">[</span><span class="token token content" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">Telegram Bot Token</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">](</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">https://t.me/BotFather</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">)</span><span> (free)
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> Installation</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token code" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">```</span><span class="token token code code-language">bash</span><span class="token token code">
</span></span><span><span class="token token code"></span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash" style="color: rgb(112, 184, 255);">git</span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash"> clone https://github.com/Adarsh-Menon/Zarik-Travel-Agency-Support.git
</span></span><span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash"></span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash" style="color: rgb(251, 173, 96);">cd</span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash"> Zarik-Travel-Agency-Support
</span></span><span>python -m venv venv
</span><span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash">venv</span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">\</span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash">Scripts</span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">\</span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash">activate           </span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash" style="color: rgb(129, 136, 152);"># Windows</span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash">
</span></span><span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash">pip </span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash" style="color: rgb(112, 184, 255);">install</span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash"> --upgrade pip
</span></span><span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash">pip </span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash" style="color: rgb(112, 184, 255);">install</span><span class="token token code code-block language-bash"> -r requirements.txt</span><span class="token token code">
</span></span><span><span class="token token code"></span><span class="token token code" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">```</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> Configuration</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token code" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">```</span><span class="token token code code-language">bash</span><span class="token token code">
