span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> Lead Management</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> Excel Structure</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span>Zarik auto-generates </span><span class="token token code-snippet code" style="color: rgb(204, 123, 244);">`data/leads.xlsx`</span><span> with formatted headers, color-coded status, frozen panes, and auto-filter.
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token table table-header-row" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">|</span><span class="token token table table-header-row table-header" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> Column </span><span class="token token table table-header-row" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">|</span><span class="token token table table-header-row table-header" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> Type </span><span class="token token table table-header-row" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">|</span><span class="token token table table-header-row table-header" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> Description </span><span class="token token table table-header-row" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">|</span><span class="token token table table-header-row">
