</span></span><span>## Example API Call
</span><span>
</span><span>```bash
</span><span>curl http://localhost:8000/api/leads/stats
</span><span># {"total": 12, "by_status": {"New": 5, "Contacted": 4, "Converted": 3}}
</span><span>
</span><span>curl -X PATCH http://localhost:8000/api/leads/ZRK-001 \
</span><span>  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
</span><span>  -d '{"status": "Converted", "notes": "Booked via WhatsApp"}'
</span><span>```</span></code></pre></div></div>
