          ease-[cubic-bezier(0.165,0.85,0.45,1)] h-8 w-8 rounded-md backdrop-blur-md _fill_10ocf_9 _ghost_10ocf_96" type="button" aria-label="Copy to clipboard" data-state="closed"><div class="relative"><div class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" style="width: 20px; height: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M12.5 3A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 14 4.5V6h1.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 17 7.5v8a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5h-8A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 6 15.5V14H4.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 12.5v-8A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 4.5 3zm1.5 9.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5H7v1.5a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.5v-8a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5H14zM4.5 4a.5.5 0 0 0-.5.5v8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.5v-8a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5z"></path></svg></div><div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center"><div class="transition-all opacity-0 scale-50" style="width: 20px; height: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="transition-all opacity-0 scale-50" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M15.188 5.11a.5.5 0 0 1 .752.626l-.056.084-7.5 9a.5.5 0 0 1-.738.033l-3.5-3.5-.064-.078a.501.501 0 0 1 .693-.693l.078.064 3.113 3.113 7.15-8.58z"></path></svg></div></div></div></button></div></div><div class="text-text-500 font-small p-3.5 pb-0">markdown</div><div class="overflow-x-auto"><pre class="code-block__code !my-0 !rounded-lg !text-sm !leading-relaxed p-3.5" style="color: rgb(234, 236, 240); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono);"><code class="language-markdown" style="color: rgb(234, 236, 240); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono); white-space: pre;"><span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222); font-weight: bold;">#</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> Memory System</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> How It Works</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span>Zarik stores a JSON file per user at </span><span class="token token code-snippet code" style="color: rgb(204, 123, 244);">`data/memory/{telegram_id}.json`</span><span>. This follows the ClawdBot memory pattern — file-based, per-user, and accumulates over time.
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> Memory Lifecycle</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">1.</span><span> </span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Load</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span> — on </span><span class="token token code-snippet code" style="color: rgb(204, 123, 244);">`/start`</span><span>, reads the user's JSON file (or creates a fresh one)
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">2.</span><span> </span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Read</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span> — greet node checks past trips for personalized welcome
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">3.</span><span> </span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Update</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span> — after itinerary generation, appends new trip and updates preferences
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">4.</span><span> </span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Save</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span> — writes back to JSON with updated </span><span class="token token code-snippet code" style="color: rgb(204, 123, 244);">`last_seen`</span><span> timestamp
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> Memory Structure</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token code" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">```</span><span class="token token code code-language">json</span><span class="token token code">
</span></span><span><span class="token token code"></span><span class="token token code code-block language-json" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">{</span><span class="token token code code-block language-json">
</span></span><span><span class="token token code code-block language-json">  </span><span class="token token code code-block language-json" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133);">"telegram_id"</span><span class="token token code code-block language-json" style="color: rgb(234, 236, 240);">:</span><span class="token token code code-block language-json"> </span><span class="token token code code-block language-json" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">123456789</span><span class="token token code code-block language-json" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">,</span><span class="token token code code-block language-json">
