</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> What Gets Remembered</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">-</span><span> Destinations visited → added to </span><span class="token token code-snippet code" style="color: rgb(204, 123, 244);">`preferred_destinations`</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">-</span><span> Budget range → updated from latest trip
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">-</span><span> Group size → updated from latest trip
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">-</span><span> Dietary needs → persisted across sessions
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">-</span><span> Travel style → derived from interests
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">-</span><span> Past itineraries → rolling window of last 10 trips
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> Returning User Experience</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token code" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">```</span><span class="token token code">
</span></span><span><span class="token token code"></span><span class="token token code code-block">First visit:  "👋 Welcome to Zarik! Where would you love to travel?"
</span></span><span>Second visit: "Welcome back, Adarsh! Last time you explored Japan.
</span><span><span class="token token code code-block">              Ready for your next adventure?"</span><span class="token token code">
</span></span><span><span class="token token code"></span><span class="token token code" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">```</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
