</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> Common Errors</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222); font-weight: bold;">###</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> `telegram.error.InvalidToken: The token was rejected`</span><span>
</span></span><span><span>Your </span><span class="token token code-snippet code" style="color: rgb(204, 123, 244);">`.env`</span><span> has quotes around the token. Remove them:</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.375rem] font-bold">Wrong</h2>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN="8751181816:AAH-xxxxx"</p>
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.375rem] font-bold">Correct</h2>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=8751181816:AAH-xxxxx</p>
<div role="group" aria-label="Code" tabindex="0" class="relative group/copy bg-bg-000/50 border-0.5 border-border-400 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-accent-100"><div class="sticky opacity-0 group-hover/copy:opacity-100 group-focus-within/copy:opacity-100 top-2 py-2 h-12 w-0 float-right"><div class="absolute right-0 h-8 px-2 items-center inline-flex z-10"><button class="inline-flex
