          ease-[cubic-bezier(0.165,0.85,0.45,1)] h-8 w-8 rounded-md backdrop-blur-md _fill_10ocf_9 _ghost_10ocf_96" type="button" aria-label="Copy to clipboard" data-state="closed"><div class="relative"><div class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" style="width: 20px; height: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M12.5 3A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 14 4.5V6h1.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 17 7.5v8a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5h-8A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 6 15.5V14H4.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 12.5v-8A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 4.5 3zm1.5 9.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5H7v1.5a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.5v-8a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5H14zM4.5 4a.5.5 0 0 0-.5.5v8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.5v-8a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5z"></path></svg></div><div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center"><div class="transition-all opacity-0 scale-50" style="width: 20px; height: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="transition-all opacity-0 scale-50" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M15.188 5.11a.5.5 0 0 1 .752.626l-.056.084-7.5 9a.5.5 0 0 1-.738.033l-3.5-3.5-.064-.078a.501.501 0 0 1 .693-.693l.078.064 3.113 3.113 7.15-8.58z"></path></svg></div></div></div></button></div></div><div class="overflow-x-auto"><pre class="code-block__code !my-0 !rounded-lg !text-sm !leading-relaxed p-3.5" style="color: rgb(234, 236, 240); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono);"><code style="color: rgb(234, 236, 240); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono); white-space: pre-wrap;"><span><span>
</span></span><span>### `groq.AuthenticationError: Invalid API Key`
</span><span>Same issue — remove quotes from `GROQ_API_KEY` in `.env`. Or the key is expired — generate a new one at [console.groq.com/keys](https://console.groq.com/keys).
</span><span>
</span><span>### `telegram.error.Conflict: terminated by other getUpdates request`
</span><span>Two instances are polling the same bot. Only one can run at a time.
</span><span>- Stop local Docker: `docker stop zarik`
</span><span>- Or stop Railway deployment
</span><span>- Clear stale connection: visit `https://api.telegram.org/bot{TOKEN}/deleteWebhook?drop_pending_updates=true`
</span><span>
</span><span>### `groq.GroqError: api_key must be set`
</span><span>On Railway/cloud, env vars aren't loaded from `.env` file. The lazy initialization fix handles this — make sure you have the latest `graph.py` and `itinerary_gen.py` that use `_get_llm()` pattern.
</span><span>
</span><span>### Bot responds with "Oops, something went wrong"
</span><span>Check logs for the actual error:
</span><span>- Local: terminal output
</span><span>- Docker: `docker logs zarik`
</span><span>- Railway: Logs tab in dashboard
</span><span>
</span><span>### Excel leads.xlsx permission error
</span><span>On Windows, close the Excel file before running the bot. Excel locks the file when open.
</span><span>
</span><span>## Useful Debug Commands
</span><span>
</span><span>```bash
</span><span># Check if bot token is valid
</span><span>curl https://api.telegram.org/bot{TOKEN}/getMe
</span><span>
</span><span># Check Groq API key
</span><span>curl -H "Authorization: Bearer gsk_xxx" https://api.groq.com/openai/v1/models
</span><span>
</span><span># Health check
</span><span>curl http://localhost:8000/health
</span><span>```</span></code></pre></div></div>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Go to your GitHub repo → <strong>Wiki</strong> tab → <strong>Create the first page</strong>. Create each page with the names I used (Home, Getting-Started, How-It-Works, Lead-Management, Memory-System, Troubleshooting). Copy-paste the content for each.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
