:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Open this HTML file in your browser — it's an animated demo that shows the full Zarik conversation flow with typing indicators, the LangGraph phase tracker at the bottom, and the tech stack pills. It loops automatically.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>To turn it into a GIF for GitHub:</strong></p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
