<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Use <a class="underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current" href="https://www.screentogif.com/">ScreenToGif</a> (free, Windows) — record the browser window for one full loop (~17 seconds)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Save as <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">demo.gif</code></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Add to your repo and put this at the top of your README:</li>
</ol>
